{"id":"api/common/ImageConfig","title":"ImageConfig","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/ImageConfig\", \"name\": \"ImageConfig\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/application/application_tokens.ts#L118-L137\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"imageconfig\">ImageConfig<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/ImageConfig#imageconfig\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label type-alias\">type-alias</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6taeqf3dwcyuew4nzn8hc9v84\">影象相關選項的設定物件。包括：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cqsz96bdvkzgk8nwg5ka6gagr\">breakpoints：整數斷點陣列，用於為回應式影象生成 srcsets。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"xzrbau8n05v9crp0t2r37bqp\">disableImageSizeWarning: 一個布林值。將其設定為 true 將停用關於過大影象的控制台警告。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cnbncdj6sigxewi9r8g3pj53d\">disableImageLazyLoadWarning: 一個布林值。將其設定為 true 將停用關於設定為\n<code>loading=\"lazy\"</code>的 LCP 影象的控制台警告。瞭解更多關於回應式影象設定的訊息，請檢視\n<a href=\"guide/image-directive\">NgOptimizedImage指南</a>。瞭解有關影象警告選項的更多訊息，請檢視\n<a href=\"errors/NG0913\">相關錯誤頁面</a>。</li>\n</ul>\n\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"type-alias-overview\">\n    <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n    type <a href=\"api/common/ImageConfig\" class=\"code-anchor\">ImageConfig</a> = {\n    breakpoints?: number[];\n    placeholderResolution?: number;\n    disableImageSizeWarning?: boolean;\n    disableImageLazyLoadWarning?: boolean;\n};\n    </code-example>\n  </section>\n\n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/IMAGE_CONFIG\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/ImageConfig#imageconfig\n - errors/NG0913\n - guide/image-directive\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/application/application_tokens.ts#L118-L137\n-->"}